headline: Should You Continue to Hold The Cooper Companies (COO)?
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Health Care Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund declined 5.06% (Institutional Shares) in the quarter, against a challenging backdrop for the broader Health Care sector, compared to a 6.19% decline for the Russell 3000 Health Care […]
